vision_analysis.question_text: In which of the following ways, if any, would you say you/your family are negatively impacted by tourism in your local area?
clickable_elements: Changes in the character of my/our community
Too much pressure on my/our community’s natural resources (e.g. through increased water and energy consumption)
Contributes to climate change due to carbon footprint and emissions
Fewer services for local residents (e.g. shops, schools etc.)
Reduced sense of belonging in my/our community
Less opportunity to visit certain local attractions, landmarks and/or events
Tourism activity means that the price of housing has increased
None of these – my family haven't experienced any adverse impacts of tourism in our area
